&lt;p&gt;Are you looking to progress and develop your nursing career?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Do you want to work for a Trust that cares about you?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If the answer is yes we’d love to hear from you.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are seeking registered nurses to join our teams within the surgical division in various specialties at both our Calderdale Royal Hospital and Huddersfield Royal Infirmary sites.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;To further support you experience &amp; development as CHFT we ensure all new staff nurses receive an intensive induction on commencement of employment, enrolled on a yearlong preceptorship program &amp; allocated to an experienced clinical preceptor. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We have posts in various specialties, including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Orthopedics &lt;br /&gt;• General Surgery &lt;br /&gt;• Head and Neck &lt;br /&gt;• Intensive Care Unit (ICU) &lt;br /&gt;• Theatre’s&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Amanda McGrath, Recruitment Support, 01484 343363 or email Amanda.McGrath@cht.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
